---
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>Portfolio Site · Marcus</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Serif+Display&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="wrapper">

      <nav>
        <span class="nav-name">Marcus David Yang | Aerospace Engineer @ UIUC</span>
        <div class="nav-links">
  <a href="/">home</a>
  
</div>
      </nav>

      <a href="/" class="back-link">← Home</a>

      <section class="hero">
        <p class="hero-label">Software · June 2026</p>
        <h1>Projects</h1>
        <p class="hero-desc">
          Developing my software skills through building projects and documentation. 
        </p>
      </section>

      <p class="section-label">Related Projects</p>
      <div class="projects">
        <a href="/projects/de-laval-nozzle" class="project-card-link">
          <div class="project-card">
            <span class="tag hardware">aerospace</span>
            <h3>CFD Analysis of a de Laval Nozzle</h3>
            <p>Designed, meshed, and simulated compressible flow through a converging-diverging nozzle using NX, SpaceClaim, ANSYS Meshing, and Fluent.</p>
            <p class="project-date">May 2026</p>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>

      <footer>
        <p>marcus · summer 2026</p>
        <a href="https://github.com" target="_blank">github ↗</a>
      </footer>

    </div>

    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

      body {
        font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
        background: #fafaf9;
        color: #1a1a18;
      }

      #wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 860px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
        padding-left: 80px;
        padding-right: 80px;
      }

      nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        padding-top: 2.5rem;
        padding-bottom: 2.5rem;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #e0dfd8;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      .nav-name {
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
      }

      .nav-links {
        display: flex;
        gap: 2rem;
      }

      .nav-links a {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888780;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .nav-links a:hover { color: #1a1a18; }

      .back-link {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #888780;
        text-decoration: none;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      }

      .back-link:hover { color: #1a1a18; }

      .hero {
        margin-bottom: 5rem;
      }

      .hero-label {
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #b4b2a9;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }

      .hero h1 {
        font-family: 'DM Serif Display', serif;
        font-size: 44px;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.15;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      }

      .hero-desc {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #5f5e5a;
        line-height: 1.7;
        max-width: 480px;
      }

      .section-label {
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #b4b2a9;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }

      .projects {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 1px;
        background: #e0dfd8;
        border: 1px solid #e0dfd8;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
      }

      .project-card-link {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        display: block;
      }

      .project-card {
        background: #fafaf9;
        padding: 1.75rem 2rem;
        height: 100%;
      }

      .project-card:hover { background: #f1efea; }

      .tag {
        display: inline-block;
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 10px;
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        padding: 3px 8px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        margin-bottom: 0.9rem;
      }

      .tag.software { background: #E6F1FB; color: #185FA5; }
      .tag.hardware { background: #E1F5EE; color: #0F6E56; }
      .tag.aerospace { background: #E1F5EE; color: #0F6E56; }

      .project-card h3 {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 500;
        margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
      }

      .project-card p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #5f5e5a;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .project-date {
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
        font-size: 11px;
        color: #b4b2a9;
        margin-top: 1rem;
      }

      footer {
        padding-top: 2rem;
        padding-bottom: 3rem;
        border-top: 1px solid #e0dfd8;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
      }

      footer p {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #b4b2a9;
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      }

      footer a {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #b4b2a9;
        font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      footer a:hover { color: #1a1a18; }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>